    "A way out is to exploit a variational lower bound L VLB for the cross entropy 56:",
    "To make the above expression computable, the expectation value can be split into its independent steps.",
    "Consequently, it can be rewritten as a summation of several Kullback-Leibler divergences, D KL, plus one entropy term (see details in Appendix B of ref. 56).",
    "In this way, L VLB becomes",
    "Article https://doi.org/10.1038/s42256-024-00810-0"
  ]
}